description: Enjoy spacious living in this oversized 2-bed, 2-bath condo with parking in desirable South Boston. This over 1,300 sq ft home boasts a huge open kitchen, living & dining area. The updated kitchen features elegant white Calcutta quartz countertops, stainless-steel appliances, & a convenient breakfast bar flowing seamlessly into the large dining space. Relax by the cozy gas fireplace in the generously-sized living area.  A thoughtful mudroom leads to your own private outdoor patio—surrounded by strategic landscaping, it is a perfect space for entertaining. The sunny master suite boasts a large built-out closet & an en suite bath with exquisite Carrara marble tile shower & vanity. The fantastic 2nd bedroom has an adjacent full bath. Notable details incl: hardwood floors throughout, direct access parking space, central AC, in-unit laundry, abundant storage within the unit plus a lg deeded storage unit. Prime location close to Broadway T, restaurants, retail, coffee and Boston's South End!
